Features
 . ASR by Google API
 . Wakeup by Snowboy
 . TTS by Google API
 . R2D2 robot control via serial communication with arduino
  : movement
  : dome control
  : LED control
  : piezo
  : button at the bottom (WIP) 
 . Chatbot with chatterbot engine
 . Object detection with opencv
 . Object tracking with opencv



Pre-requite
 . sox and sox mp3 extension
 . libc5.0 support for ubuntu 14.04
 . portaudio
 . ??? package to prevent SSH related warning messages

pip install urllib3[secure]

ROS module
 . ASR (as a service)
 . Wakeup
 . TTS
 . Chatbot (as a service)
 . Arduino Serial
 . Vision - Face
 . Vision - SSD
 . Neocortex

